BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:cardio-long-run@workout-calendar.rowlandpettit
DTSTAMP:20260607T155209Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260607T155209Z
SEQUENCE:0
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260613T090000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260613T101500
RRULE:FREQ=WEEKLY
SUMMARY:Run: Long Easy 4-6 mi
DESCRIPTION:Long run starts at 9:00 AM.\n\nGoal:\n- 4-6 miles easy\, conver
 sational pace.\n- Start near 4 miles. Hold 4-6 miles for the first few we
 eks before building.\n- No pace chasing. This is discipline and aerobic b
 ase.\n\nSimple progression:\n- Weeks 1-2: 4 miles.\n- Weeks 3-4: 5 miles.
 \n- Weeks 5+: 6 miles if recovering well.\n- Every fourth week: cut back 
 to 4 miles.\n\nMinimum version:\n- 30 min easy run/walk.
LOCATION:Outside or treadmill
CATEGORIES:FITNESS,CARDIO,RUN
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:cardio-long-swim@workout-calendar.rowlandpettit
DTSTAMP:20260607T155209Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260607T155209Z
SEQUENCE:0
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260614T090000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260614T100000
RRULE:FREQ=WEEKLY
SUMMARY:Swim: Structured Long Swim
DESCRIPTION:Long swim starts at 9:00 AM. Smooth\, structured\, not just wan
 dering around the pool.\n\nWarm-up:\n- 200 easy.\n- 4 x 50 drill/build: c
 atch-up\, fingertip drag\, kick\, choice.\n\nMain set:\n- Ladder: 100\, 2
 00\, 300\, 200\, 100 with 20 sec rest.\n- 4 x 100 as 75 smooth + 25 stron
 g\, 20 sec rest.\n\nCool-down:\n- 100 easy.\n\nTotal:\n- Full version: ab
 out 1\,700.\n- Short version: stop after the ladder\, about 1\,100.\n\nMi
 nimum version:\n- 20-30 min relaxed swim\, keep moving\, leave feeling be
 tter.
LOCATION:Pool
CATEGORIES:FITNESS,CARDIO,SWIM
END:VEVENT
